<?php

$RayDalioPrinciples = new Chunk("principle","Ray Dalio Principles","https://www.nateliason.com/notes/principles-ray-dalio");
$RayDalioPrinciples->included = false; // don't show this by default

$category = "Life: Embrace Reality and Deal With It";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Truth, an accurate understanding of reality, is the essential foundation for any good outcome.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't get hung up on your views about how things should be because then you'll miss out on learning how they really are.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Evolution is the single greatest force in the universe; it is the only thing that is permanent and it drives everything.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Evolve or die.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Evolving is life's greatest accomplishment and its greatest reward.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Remember \"no pain, no gain\" Evolution won't always feel good.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Pain plus Reflection equals Progress. If you can develop a reflexive action to psychic pain that causes you to reflect on it rather than avoid it, it will lead to your rapid learning and evolving. If you push through this process of personal evolution, you will naturally ascend to higher and higher levels. Go towards the pain rather than avoid it. The quality of your life will depend on the choices you make at those painful moments.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Weigh second and third-order consequences. Often the first order consequences are the temptations that cost us what we really want, and can be the barriers that stand in our way.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Think of yourself as a machine operating within a machine and know that you have the ability to alter your machines to produce better outcomes.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Distinguish between you as the designer of your machine and you as a worker with your machine.");

$category = "Life: Five-Step Process";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Prioritize: you can have anything you want, but you can't have everything you want.","Have clear goals");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't confuse goals with desires. A goal is something you need to achieve. Desires tend to be things you want that stand in the way of your goals.","Have clear goals");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Never rule out a goal because you think it's unattainable.","Have clear goals");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't mistake the trappings of success with success itself.","Have clear goals");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Knowing how to deal with your setbacks is as important as knowing how to move forward","Have clear goals");

$category = "Life: Five-Step Process";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "View painful problems as potential improvements that are screaming at you.","Identify and Don't Tolerate Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't mistake the cause of the problem with the real problem. Get to the root of it.","Identify and Don't Tolerate Problems");

$category = "Life: Five-Step Process";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Focus on \"what is\" before deciding \"what to do about it\"","Diagnose problems to get at their root causes");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Distinguish proximate from root causes (I didn't check the train schedule -> I didn't check the train schedule because I'm forgetful)","Diagnose problems to get at their root causes");

$category = "Life: Five-Step Process";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Think about your problem as a set of outcomes produced by a machine.","Design a plan");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Remember that there are typically many paths to achieving your goals, you only need to find one that works.","Design a plan");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Write down your plan for everyone to see and to measure your progress against.","Design a plan");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Recognize that it doesn't take a lot of time to design a good plan. It's necessary to design a plan, though, and not get caught up in execution.","Design a plan");

$category = "Life: Five-Step Process";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Good work habits are underrated.","Push through to completion");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Establish clear metrics to make sure you're following your plan.","Push through to completion");

$category = "Life: Five-Step Process";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Remember that all weaknesses don't matter if you find solutions.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Look at the pattern of your mistakes and identify at which step in the five-step process you typically fail.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Everyone has at least one big thing that stands in the way of their success. Find yours and deal with it.");

$category = "Life: Be Radically Open Minded";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Teach your brain to work in a way that doesn't come naturally (like the creative designing an organization system).","Recognize your two barriers: your ego and your blind spots.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Use compensating mechanisms (like programmed reminders).","Recognize your two barriers: your ego and your blind spots.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Rely on the help of others who are strong where they are weak.","Recognize your two barriers: your ego and your blind spots.");

$category = "Life: Be Radically Open Minded";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Decision making is a two-step process: First take in all the relevant information, then decide.","Practice radical open-mindedness");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't worry about looking good, worry about achieving your goals.","Practice radical open-mindedness");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "You're looking for the best answer, not simply the best answer that you can come up with yourself.","Practice radical open-mindedness");

$category = "Life: Be Radically Open Minded";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Open-mindedness isn't easy because of your lizard brain, so you have to practice taking feedback impersonally.","Appreciate the art of thoughtful disagreement");

$category = "Life Principle";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Understand that People are Wired Very Differently");

$category = "Life: Learn How to Make Decisions Effectively";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Recognize that the biggest threat to good decision making is harmful emotions, and the decision making is a two-step process (first learning, then deciding)");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Failing to consider second and third order consequences is the cause of a lot of painfully bad decisions, and it is especially deadly when the first inferior option confirms your own biases.");

$category = "Life: Learn How to Make Decisions Effectively";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "One of the most important decisions you can make is who you ask questions of","Synthesize the situation at hand");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't believe everything you hear","Synthesize the situation at hand");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Everything looks bigger up close: what's happening today seems like a bigger deal than it will in retrospect","Synthesize the situation at hand");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "New is overvalued relative to great","Synthesize the situation at hand");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't over squeeze dots","Synthesize the situation at hand");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Think of each decision as a bet with a probability and a reward for being right and a probability and a penalty for being wrong.","Make your decisions as expected value calculations");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Sometimes it's smart to take a chance even when the odds are overwhelmingly against you if the cost of being wrong is negligible relative to the reward that comes with the slim chance of being right. \"It never hurts to ask.\"","Make your decisions as expected value calculations");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "The best choices are the ones that have more pros than cons, not those that don't have any cons at all.","Make your decisions as expected value calculations");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "All of your must-dos must be done before you do any of your \"like-to-dos\"
","Prioritize by weighing the value of additional information against the cost of not deciding.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "You won't have time to deal with unimportant things, which is better than not having time to deal with important things.","Prioritize by weighing the value of additional information against the cost of not deciding.");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Slow down your thinking so you can note the criteria you are using to make your decision. Write the criteria down as a principle. Think about those criteria when you have an outcome to assess, and refine them before the next \"one of those\" comes along.","Use Principles");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Convert your principles into algorithms and have the computer make decisions alongside you","Use Principles");


$category = "Work";
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "In order to be great, one can't compromise the uncompromisable.");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Make your passion and your work one and the same and do it with people you want to be with.");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Realize that you have nothing to fear from knowing the truth.","Trust in Radical Truth and Radical Transparency");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Never say anything about someone that you wouldn't say to them directly and don't try people without accusing them to their faces.","Trust in Radical Truth and Radical Transparency");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Cultivate Meaningful Work and Meaningful Relationships");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Fail well. Everyone fails, so fail well.","Create a Culture in Which It Is Okay to Make Mistakes and Unacceptable Not to Learn From Them");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Get over \"blame\" and \"credit\" and get on with \"accurate\" and \"inaccurate.\"","Create a Culture in Which It Is Okay to Make Mistakes and Unacceptable Not to Learn From Them");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Remember to reflect when you experience pain.","Create a Culture in Which It Is Okay to Make Mistakes and Unacceptable Not to Learn From Them");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Know that nobody can see themselves objectively.","Create a Culture in Which It Is Okay to Make Mistakes and Unacceptable Not to Learn From Them");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Be open-minded and assertive at the same time.","Get and Stay in Sync");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Watch out for people who think it's embarrassing not to know.","Get and Stay in Sync");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "If it's your meeting, manage the conversation","Get and Stay in Sync");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Meetings: Watch out for topic slip","Get and Stay in Sync");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Meetings: Let people talk for two minutes before being interruptible","Get and Stay in Sync");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Find the most believable people possible who disagree with you and try to understand their reasoning","Believability Weight Your Decision Making");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Remember that believable opinions are most likely to come from people who have successfully accomplished the thing in question at least three times, and who have great explanation of the cause-effect relationships that lead them to their conclusions.","Believability Weight Your Decision Making");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Pay more attention to people's reasoning for a conclusion than their specific conclusion","Believability Weight Your Decision Making");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Think about whether you're playing the role of a teacher, student, or peer, and whether you should be teaching, asking questions, or debating.","Believability Weight Your Decision Making");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Understand how people came by their opinions","Believability Weight Your Decision Making");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "If you ask someone a question, they'll give you an answer, so think through who you should address your question to.","Believability Weight Your Decision Making");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Pay more attention to whether the decision-making system is fair than whether you get your way.","Believability Weight Your Decision Making");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Principles can't be ignored by mutual agreement.","Recognize How to Get Beyond Disagreement");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't leave important conflicts unresolved.","Recognize How to Get Beyond Disagreement");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Once a decision is made, everyone should get behind it even though individuals may still disagree.","Recognize How to Get Beyond Disagreement");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Remember that WHO is more important than WHAT");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Match the person with the design","Hire Right, Because the Penalties for Hiring Wrong are Huge");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Think through which values, abilities, and skills you are looking for (in that order).","Hire Right, Because the Penalties for Hiring Wrong are Huge");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Look for people who sparkle, not just \"any of those\" ","Hire Right, Because the Penalties for Hiring Wrong are Huge");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Pay attention to people's track records.","Hire Right, Because the Penalties for Hiring Wrong are Huge");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Recognize that performance in school doesn't tell you much about whether a person has the values and abilities you are looking for.","Hire Right, Because the Penalties for Hiring Wrong are Huge");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't hire people just to fit the first job they will do. Hire people you want to share your life with.","Hire Right, Because the Penalties for Hiring Wrong are Huge");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "When considering compensation, provide both stability and opportunity","Hire Right, Because the Penalties for Hiring Wrong are Huge");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Focus more on making the pie bigger than on exactly how to slice it so that you or anyone else gets the biggest piece.","Hire Right, Because the Penalties for Hiring Wrong are Huge");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Great people are hard to find so make sure you think about how to keep them.","Hire Right, Because the Penalties for Hiring Wrong are Huge");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Understand that you and the people you manage will go through a process of personal evolution.","Constantly Train, Test, Evaluate, and Sort People");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Recognize that personal evolution should be relatively rapid and a natural consequence of discovering one's strengths and weaknesses; as a result. Career paths are not planned at the outset.","Constantly Train, Test, Evaluate, and Sort People");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Evaluate accurately, not kindly","Constantly Train, Test, Evaluate, and Sort People");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Think about accuracy, not implications","Constantly Train, Test, Evaluate, and Sort People");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't hide your observations about people.","Constantly Train, Test, Evaluate, and Sort People");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Use evaluation tools such as performance surveys, metrics, and formal reviews to document all aspects of a person's performance.","Constantly Train, Test, Evaluate, and Sort People");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "When you are really in sync with someone about their weaknesses, the weaknesses are probably true","Constantly Train, Test, Evaluate, and Sort People");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Evaluate employees with the same rigor as you evaluate job candidates","Constantly Train, Test, Evaluate, and Sort People");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't lower the bar","Constantly Train, Test, Evaluate, and Sort People");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "No matter what work you do, at a high level you are simply setting goals and building machines to help you achieve them.","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "For every case you deal with, your approach should have two purposes: To move you closer to your goal. To train and test your machine","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Clearly assign responsibilities","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Watch out for job slip","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Probe deep and hard to learn what you can expect from your machine","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Use daily updates as a tool for staying on top of what your people are doing and thinking.","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't assume that people's answers are correct. You occasionally need to double check them.","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Pull all suspicious threads","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Recognize and deal with key-man risk. Every key person should have someone who can replace them.","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Great leadership is generally not what it is made out to be. Being maximally effective is the most important thing that a leader must do. It is more practical to be honest about one's uncertainties, mistakes, and weaknesses than to pretend they don't exist. It is also more important to have good challengers than good followers.","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't give orders and try to be followed, try to be understood and to understand others by getting in sync.","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Hold yourself and your people accountable and appreciate them for holding you accountable","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "If you've agreed with someone that something is supposed to go a certain way, make sure it goes that way, unless you get in sync about doing it differently.","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Communicate the plan clearly and have clear metrics conveying whether you are progressing according to it.","Manage as Someone Operating a Machine to Achieve a Goal");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Problems are like coal thrown into a locomotive engine because burning them up-inventing and implementing solutions for them-propels us forward. Every problem you find is an opportunity to improve your machine. Identifying and not tolerating problems is one of the most important and disliked things people can do.","Perceive and Don't Tolerate Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "If you're not worried, you need to worry. And if you're worried, you don't need to worry.","Perceive and Don't Tolerate Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Design and oversee a machine to perceive whether things are good enough or not good enough, or do it yourself.","Perceive and Don't Tolerate Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Watch out for the frog boiling in the water syndrome.","Perceive and Don't Tolerate Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Taste the soup, make sure it tastes good before going out to the customer","Perceive and Don't Tolerate Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't be afraid to fix the difficult things","Perceive and Don't Tolerate Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Think of the problems you perceive in a machinelike way","Perceive and Don't Tolerate Problems");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "To diagnose well, ask the following questions: Is the outcome good or bad? Who is responsible for the outcome (RP)? If the outcome is bad, is the RP incapable and/or is the design bad?","Diagnose Problems to Get at Their Root Causes");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Just because someone else doesn't know what to do doesn't mean that you do know what to do.","Diagnose Problems to Get at Their Root Causes");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Use the following drill down technique to gain an eighty / twenty understanding of a department or sub-department that is having problems: List the problems, inventory all the core problems. Be specific. Name names. Don't try to find solutions yet. Identify the root causes. Keep asking \"Why?\". Create a plan that addresses the root causes. Execute the plan and transparently track its progress.","Diagnose Problems to Get at Their Root Causes");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Understand that diagnosis is foundational to both progress and quality relationships","Diagnose Problems to Get at Their Root Causes");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Build your machine. Observe what you're doing and why, extrapolate the relevant principles from the cases at hand, and systemizing that process. It takes longer to build a machine than to complete a task, but it pays off over the long run.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Build the organization around goals rather than tasks.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't build the organization to fit the people.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Make departments as self-sufficient as possible so that they have control over the resources they need to achieve their goals.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Don't just pay attention to your job; pay attention to how your job will be done if you're no longer around.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Use \"double-do\" rather than \"double-check\" to make sure mission-critical tasks are done correctly.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Create an organizational chart to look like a pyramid, with straight lines down that don't cross.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Keep your strategic vision the same while making appropriate tactical changes as circumstances dictate.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Have good controls so that you are not exposed to the dishonesty of others.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Use public hangings to deter bad behavior.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Have the clearest possible reporting lines and delineations of responsibilities.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Constantly think about how to produce leverage.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Remember that almost everything will take more time and cost more money than you expect.","Design Improvements to Your Machine to Get Around Your Problems");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Work for goals that you and your organization are excited aboutâ€¦ and think about how your tasks connect to those goals.","Do What You Set Out to Do");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Use checklists","Do What You Set Out to Do");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "When you hit your goals, celebrate!","Do What You Set Out to Do");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Having systemized principles embedded in tools is especially valuable for an idea meritocracy","Use Tools and Protocols to Shape How Work is Done");

$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "All organizations must have checks and balances.","Don't Overlook Governance");
$RayDalioPrinciples->addNugget($category, "Make sure that no one is more powerful than the system or so important that they are irreplaceable.","Don't Overlook Governance");

$Wisdom->addChunk($RayDalioPrinciples);
